h. Description based on: Anno. VII, No. 15 (April 17, 1920); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed May 1, 2019). Latest issue consulted: Anno XVII, No. 51 (20 Dicembre 1930) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed May 1, 2019)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:47.120Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2019271083/", "image_url": [], "index": 4, "language": ["italian", "english"], "location": ["fairfield", "bridgeport", "connecticut", "fairfield county", "united states"], "number": ["2019271083", "online resource", "1099570284", "2643-5101", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Sentinel"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "la sentinella = the sentinel (bridgeport, conn.) 191?-1948 [online resource]", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 44.85431, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["bridgeport", "fairfield", "connecticut", "newspapers", "italian", "fairfield county (conn.)", "bridgeport (conn.)", "italians", "fairfield county", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:58:32.070Z", "title": "La sentinella = The sentinel", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2019271083/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2019271086/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1906", "dates": ["[1906 TO 1908]"], "description": ["Weekly Began with anno I, num. 1 (3 Marzo 1906); ceased with anno II, no. 44 (9 Dicembre 1908). Includes sections titled: La Tribuna di Port Chester, N.Y., ag. 11, 1906-nov. 1907, and: La Tribuna di Dambury [i.e. Danbury], magg. 2-ott. 24, 1908, and: La Tribuna di Portchester, dic. 1908. Suspended with ott. 24, 1908 issue: resumed with nov. 25, 1908 issue. Also issued on microfilm from Connecticut State Library, Hartford, CT. In Italian, 1906-1908. In Ita